            <fr:title text="Interior">Interior</fr:title>
            <fr:taxon>Definition</fr:taxon>
          </fr:frontmatter>
          <fr:mainmatter>
            <html:p>
The <html:strong>interior</html:strong> of a subset <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[S]]></fr:tex> of a <fr:link href="/gtop-0002/" title="Topological Space" uri="https://boatnotabot.com/gtop-0002/" display-uri="gtop-0002" type="local">topological space</fr:link> <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[X]]></fr:tex> is the union of all subsets of <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[S]]></fr:tex> that are open in <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[X]]></fr:tex>.
</html:p>
            <fr:tree show-metadata="false">
              <fr:frontmatter>
                <fr:authors>
                  <fr:author>
                    <fr:link href="/boat/" title="Zihang Zeng" uri="https://boatnotabot.com/boat/" display-uri="boat" type="local">Zihang Zeng</fr:link>
